"     (Zoloft Oral)",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:4em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     25 mg (30): $168.86",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:4em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     50 mg (30): $168.86",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:4em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     100 mg (30): $168.86",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block mop drugH1Div\" id=\"F220655\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Monitoring Parameters",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Monitor nutritional intake and weight; mental status for depression, suicide ideation (especially at the beginning of therapy or when doses are increased or decreased), anxiety, social functioning, mania, panic attacks; signs/symptoms of serotonin syndrome;  akathisia; growth in pediatric patients",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
